term: The period of time to pay off the loan (month)
dti: Monthly debt payments divided by the gross monthly income (%)
delinq_2yrs: The number of times of 30+ days past due on a payment in the past 2 years
inq_last_6mths: Number of credit inquiries in the last 6 months
open_acc: The number of open credit lines currently in the credit file
pub_rec: Number of derogatory public records (e.g., crime records)
revol_bal: The unpaid balance amount, if the balance on revolving credit account is not paid in full ($)
revol_util: The amount of credit used relative to all available revolving credit (%)
total_acc: The total number of credit lines currently in the credit file
application_type: Whether the loan is an individual application or a joint application with two co-borrowers
